yawf (2.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix WebKit memory pressure thresholds that never fired before OOM crash.
  * Dynamic memory limit (40% of RAM) and 5 s polling instead of 30 s.
  * Enable JSC concurrent and generational GC for smoother message storms.
  * Auto-reload after 4 hours idle to reclaim accumulated JS heap.
  * Add Refresh option to system tray context menu.
  * Tighten unresponsive detection from 5 s to 3 s.
  * Stop loading WebInspector bundle by default (set YAWF_DEVTOOLS=1 to enable).

 -- Wahid7852 <wahidzk0091@gmail.com>  Sat, 28 Jun 2026 02:30:00 +0530

